<c id="ref324" level="series"> <did> <unittitle>Poetry</unittitle> <unitid>Series VI.</unitid> <unitid type="aspace_uri">/repositories/2/archival_objects/208735</unitid> <unitdate datechar="creation" type="inclusive">1940-1966, undated</unitdate> </did> <scopecontent id="aspace_8c205ecf697c4cde88ce5b4a8c5053a7"> <head>Scope and Contents</head> <p>The poetry series includes poems by Thomas Merton as well as poems by Raissa Maritain and Rafael Alberti which were translated by Thomas Merton. Most of the poems are about spirituality, yet some reflect American culture like an Ode to Ernest Hemingway. The collection concludes with a file containing many draft works by the famous American poet Robert Lax. Lax was a close childhood friend of Merton's and sent him many poems in his minimalist style.</p> </scopecontent> <c id="ref325" level="file"/> <c id="ref326" level="file"/> <c id="ref327" level="file"/> <c id="ref328" level="file"/> <c id="ref329" level="file"/> <c id="ref330" level="file"/> <c id="ref331" level="file"/> <c id="ref332" level="file"/> <c id="ref333" level="file"/> <c id="ref334" level="file"/> <c id="ref335" level="file"/> <c id="ref336" level="file"/> <c id="ref337" level="file"/> <c id="ref338" level="file"/> <c id="ref339" level="file"/> <c id="ref340" level="file"/> <c id="ref341" level="file"/> <c id="ref342" level="file"/> <c id="ref343" level="file"/> <c id="ref344" level="file"/> <c id="ref345" level="file"/> <c id="ref346" level="file"/> <c id="ref347" level="file"/> <c id="ref348" level="file"/> <c id="ref349" level="file"/> <c id="ref350" level="file"/> <c id="ref351" level="file"/> <c id="ref352" level="file"/> <c id="ref353" level="file"/> <c id="ref354" level="file"/> <c id="ref355" level="file"/> <c id="ref356" level="file"/> <c id="ref357" level="file"/> <c id="ref358" level="file"/> <c id="ref359" level="file"/> <c id="ref360" level="file"/> <c id="ref361" level="file"/> <c id="ref362" level="file"/> <c id="ref363" level="file"/> <c id="r